  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2023-04-06",
    "date": "2024-02-01T13:45:22Z",
    "text": "Ensuring Safer Schools Act of 2023\n\nThis bill allows funds under the Community Oriented Policing Services (COPS) grant program to be used to hire and train veterans and retired law enforcement officers as school resource officers. It also directs the Department of Veterans Affairs to coordinate with COPS grant recipients to connect veterans seeking to serve as school resource officers with local law enforcement agencies participating in school-based partnerships."
